{"tid":2302523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"徐英偉：「青年內地實習資助(送錢)計劃」提供騰訊、華為、大疆及螞蟻金服等的實習崗位","createTime":"2020-11-27T07:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T08:46:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ee882bb4bb49db7522974c9f7edf89786859fec6","tid":2302523,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"徐英偉：各項內地實習計位將進一步擴展<br />\n<br />\n施政報告提出支持本港青年到粵港澳大灣區發展，民政事務局長徐英偉在記者會指，當局會在疫情穩定後推出各種實習及交流資助計劃，而「內地專題實習計劃」 進一步將項目擴展到航天科技、生態、文化保育及考古研究等領域。他說，「青年內地實習資助計劃」提供騰訊、華為、大疆及螞蟻金服等的實習崗位，而資助計劃下的「粵港澳大灣區香港青年實習計劃」涵蓋所有大灣區城市。<br />\n<br />\n在藝術方面，徐英偉指當局會成立「藝術科技專責小組」，專責提升藝利及科技的多樣性 、凝聚資源，又在東九文化中心試驗場地，配置創新科技器材，作為藝術及科技結合的場所。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2368250&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpCKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=6e7cf270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368250</a>"},{"pid":"e128078a7695d1ab51d08be2bf550a957005b37c","tid":2302523,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:40:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"220fd9dba4da99b2d556307d00670b9e168cad34","tid":2302523,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6o6MaBC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6o6MaBC.gif&h=c9607334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2283a013424b2fcf3efec21d873bdb0ac098558b","tid":2302523,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"包埋叫雞先會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26b473235e6984f7d64a65a484856d853530a3e","tid":2302523,"uid":224510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:42:42.000Z","msg":"女同學被陪訓<img src=\"/assets/fac